public final class ClusterContextTable

Table of agent addresses on this VM, allowing static deserialization threads to find their agent's address.

withEmptyClusterContext

public static final void withEmptyClusterContext(java.lang.Runnable thunk)
May be used by non-society classes to provide an empty context for deserialization of objects sent from within a society. The resulting instances may still be "broken" in various ways, wrapping this call around the deserialization will at least allow avoiding warning messages. WARNING: This must never be used within society code.
